unner, and as Yinsen in the film adaptation of the Iron Man comic book series.\n\nToub, who is of Persian Jewish background, was born in Tehran, Iran and raised in Manchester, England (his family left Iran before the 1979 revolution). At the age of fourteen, he moved to Switzerland and after a two year stay, he crossed the Atlantic to Nashua, New Hampshire to finish his last year of high school. His high school yearbook notes: \"The funniest guy in school and the most likely to succeed in the entertainment world.\" After two years of college in Massachusetts, Shaun transferred to USC.\n\nShaun is active in the Iranian Jewish community. Through various charity events and public speaking engagements, he inspires the community to embrace the arts, as the arts enhance everyday life. He has been a recipient of the Sephard award at the Los Angeles Sephardic Film Festival. Toub currently resides in Los Angeles.","name":"Shaun Toub","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"숀 토브","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"肖恩·托布（Shaun Toub）是一位伊朗裔美国电影和电视演员。他最出名的可能是他在 2004 年的电影《撞车》中饰演法哈德，在电影《追风筝的人》中饰演拉希姆汗，以及在钢铁侠漫画系列改编的电影中饰演尹森。\n\n托布有波斯犹太背景，出生于伊朗德黑兰，在英国曼彻斯特长大（他的家人在 1979 年革命前离开伊朗）。十四岁时，他移居瑞士，在呆了两年后，他横渡大西洋来到新罕布什尔州的纳舒厄，完成了高中的最后一年。他的高中年鉴写道：“学校里最有趣的人，最有可能在娱乐界取得成功。在马萨诸塞州上了两年大学后，肖恩转学到南加州大学。\n\n肖恩活跃于伊朗犹太社区。通过各种慈善活动和公开演讲活动，他鼓励社区拥抱艺术，因为艺术改善了日常生活。他曾获得洛杉矶塞法迪电影节的塞法德奖。托布目前居住在洛杉矶。","name":"肖恩·托布","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Шаун Тоуб","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IN","iso_639_1":"ml","name":"","english_name":"Malayalam","data":{"biography":"","name":"ഷോണ്‍ തൗബ്","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"ฌอน ทูบ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Шон Тоуб","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"شان طوب","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"שון טוב","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"ショーン・トーブ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"","name":"Σάουν Τουμπ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"شاون طوب","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BY","iso_639_1":"be","name":"беларуская мова","english_name":"Belarusian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Шон Тоўб","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"肖恩·託布（Shaun Toub）是一位伊朗裔美國電影和電視演員。他最出名的可能是他在 2004 年的電影《撞車》中飾演法哈德，在電影《追風箏的孩子》中飾演拉希姆汗，以及在鐵甲奇俠漫畫系列改編的電影中飾演尹森。\n\n託布有波斯猶太背景，出生於伊朗德黑蘭，在英國曼徹斯特長大（他的家人在 1979 年革命前離開伊朗）。十四歲時，他移居瑞士，在呆了兩年後，他橫渡大西洋來到新罕布什爾州的納舒厄，完成了高中的最後一年。他的高中年鑑寫道：“學校裏最有趣的人，最有可能在娛樂界取得成功。在馬薩諸塞州上了兩年大學後，肖恩轉學到南加州大學。\n\n肖恩活躍於伊朗猶太社區。透過 通過各種慈善活動和公開演講活動，他鼓勵社區擁抱藝術，因為藝術改善了日常生活。他曾獲得洛杉磯塞法迪電影節的塞法德獎。託布目前居住在洛杉磯。","name":"肖恩·託布","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PK","iso_639_1":"ur","name":"اردو","english_name":"Urdu","data":{"biography":"","name":"شون توب","primary":false}}]}},"tv_298196_keywords":{"at":1772469971925,"data":{"id":298196,"results":[]}},"tv_283682_credits":{"at":1772469976965,"data":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":131343,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Mei Ting","original_name":"梅婷","popularity":1.3125,"profile_path":"/90RGl03U4aRAHmpUuDMsal3NzSi.jpg","chara